'''Chrono Trigger''' is a critically acclaimed RPG developed by Square, featuring time travel mechanics and multiple endings.

==Overview==

Developed by the "Dream Team" of:
* Hironobu Sakaguchi (Final Fantasy creator)
* Yuji Horii (Dragon Quest creator)  
* Akira Toriyama (Dragon Ball artist)

